All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Account
The Account class represent account, used in auction this user is holding all functionalities and data needed to have in users.
Accounts
The Accounts interface is representing wrapper for all account types.
AccountsManager
The AccountsManager class represent manager to all users.
Admin
The Admin class is inheriting class Auctioner, representing user type admin.
AdminController
The AdminController class represent controller for AdminZone.
Auction
The Auction class represents one auction session.
Auctioner
The Auctioner class is inheriting class Auctioner, representing user type auctioner.
AuctionerController
The AuctionerController class represent controller for AuctionerZone.
AuctionPane
The AuctionPane class is used as main window for auction, it is component of design pattern observer.
AuctionSetup
The AuctionSetup interface represent wrapper for strategy types.
BuyController
The BuyController class representing controller for BuyWindow, in which user can see process of auction, and provide ability to bid.
Controller
The Controller class representing controller for multiple GUIs.
CountDownLabel
The CountDownLabel class representing part of observer design patter.
ExternalAuction
The ExternalAuction class represent preimplemented class for second type of auction working with bots agaist users
InternalAuction
The InternalAuction class is one type for strategy design pattern.
MainGUI
The MainGUI class contain function main so it is most important class for functional application.
NFT
The NFT interface is important interface for products.
NFT.typeGif
Nested interface user specially as interface for type NftGif
Nft2D
The Nft2D class represent one basic type of NFT.
Nft3D
The Nft3D class represent one type of NFT.
NftGif
The NftGif class represent one type of NFT.
NftManager<T extends Nft2D>
The NftManager class crucial for managing work with NFTs.
NotEnoughUsersException
The NotEnoughUsersException class inherit class Exception and is used as new exception, later thrown when too few users are in system to start auction
PreAuctionerController
The PreAuctionerController is class, which represents controller for auctioner.
TimeCountdown
The TimeCountdown class is instance of thread.
UserMenuController
The UserMenuController is class, which represents controller for user.
